    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/66867e51e099de06d98a98bbd190004a.poster.avif?t=1767353181\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/66867e51e099de06d98a98bbd190004a.webm?t=1767353181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/66867e51e099de06d98a98bbd190004a.mp4?t=1767353181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Captain Edgar</strong> 是一款引人入胜的FTD游戏，让您沉浸在一名宇航员的生活中，探索一个神秘的反乌托邦世界。（同时包含FPS、塔防、基地建设等多种元素。）<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong>Captain Edgar</strong> 的故事开始于一个污染严重且资源枯竭的地球，生命即将走到尽头。人类的希望寄托在寻找一个新的宜居星球上。您的任务是在这个外星前哨站上生存下来，将其转变成人类的避风港，并抵御夜间的袭击。一切都在威胁着您：星球上的野生动物、入侵的物种、恶劣的环境，甚至其他幸存者。无论付出什么代价，都要再度度过一个夜晚。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/fc9f8cfa7d3f8ee5409ef1ad6cc9ca27.poster.avif?t=1767353181\" width=600 height=223 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/fc9f8cfa7d3f8ee5409ef1ad6cc9ca27.webm?t=1767353181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/ca88f7c21a91a22b948bf7d3973ec298.webp?t=1767353181\" width=616 height=1 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/e6df55d0983a89cd4e40f655f4e2ac44.avif?t=1767353181\" width=616 height=185 /></span><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >前哨站建设</h2>探索这个未知的世界，收集必要的资源，组合并升级您的前哨站单位，建立自己的堡垒。<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掠夺与农耕</h2>在探索模式中，收集矿物和环境资源，体验独特的开放世界。通过传送带和机器自动化收集和处理资源，从机器人农场到环境改造系统。<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >模拟电脑</h2>通过您的胶囊模拟电脑连接到卫星，设计并建造可以防御您的区域或管理行星资源的前哨站。培养机器人农场，管理电力，升级您的车辆，并自定义从前哨站的旗帜到名字的一切。<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特武器</h2>充分利用独特的ZEN枪械及其不同的原渣属性，并使用性能各异的弹药。确保您为夜晚做好了无缝的准备。<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >夜间守卫</h2>当夜幕降临，武器出鞘，冲突通过流血来解决。市民们，组织您的宇航员民兵，建立您的基地防御系统，并坚守到天亮——但每一晚都会比上一晚更加血腥。<br><br>在这个反乌托邦世界中，每一个决定都至关重要。您能在经济与防御之间找到正确的平衡吗？您需要更多的宇航员士兵、更高级的基地，还是额外的生产设施？您会用武器抵御敌人，还是驾驶车辆冲向他们？这将是一个艰难的夜晚，但看到您的基地在日出时仍然屹立并生存到另一个白天，价值无可估量。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/ca88f7c21a91a22b948bf7d3973ec298.webp?t=1767353181\" width=616 height=1 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/9aa9297d74a1acde707c824e4848c4f2.avif?t=1767353181\" width=616 height=185 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/6428133a16075b775d9397440673fdc2.avif?t=1767353181\" width=616 height=300 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/ca88f7c21a91a22b948bf7d3973ec298.webp?t=1767353181\" width=616 height=1 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/b4dca3375c2d77328f27594702d1ceae.avif?t=1767353181\" width=616 height=185 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/88b85e8ecf7d35d459dffe04b166b7fe.webp?t=1767353181\" width=616 height=34 /></span><br>在<i>Captain Edgar®: Giza</i>中，音效不仅仅是音效；它们是表达我们游戏风格和激励他人的方式。这些声音不仅是项目末尾匆忙添加的额外内容；它们与主角一样，是游戏体验的核心。这些声音由一家充满激情的工作室精心录制。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/ca88f7c21a91a22b948bf7d3973ec298.webp?t=1767353181\" width=616 height=1 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/14c9ad8ac5f40d146593778f1020acac.avif?t=1767353181\" width=616 height=160 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682040/extras/c63e769cc534a81d2c9a3ec600bb4a47.webp?t=1767353181\" width=616 height=34 /></span><br>这款游戏是一个由小团队开发的充满激情的项目。我们计划添加一个庞大的银河系和合作系统。请与我们联系，分享您的想法、意见和建议——我们在倾听您的反馈。</li></ul>",
